'''Luis Jorge Mayser Ardaya''' (born July 21, 1928, San Ignacio de Velasco, [[Santa Cruz Department (Bolivia)|Santa Cruz]]) is a [[Bolivia]]n politician. He is the general secretary of the [[Bolivian Socialist Falange]] (FSB).<ref name="par"/> Mayser joined FSB at the age of twelve.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eldiario.net/noticias/2009/2009_02/nt090217/1_03opn.php|title=Noticias EL DIARIO - Primera página|work=eldiario.net}}</ref>
Mayser was elected to the Chamber of Deputies in 1997, from the single-member constituency 58 in Santa Cruz (covering areas in the provinces Velasco, Chiquitos, Angel Sandoval and German Busch) on a [[Nationalist Democratic Action]] (ADN) ticket. At the time he was the sole FSB parliamentarian.<ref name="par">''Directorio: 1997 - 2002''. La Paz: Centro de Investigación del Congreso Nacional (CICON), 2002. p. 138</ref><ref>http://www.cne.org.bo/proces_electoral/generales/resultados97/candidatos/partido.asp?sig=ADN</ref>
In 2004 Mayser was awarded the title "''hijo ilustre''" by the Santa Cruz de la Sierra municipal council, for his role in founding the Comité Pro Santa Cruz.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eldeber.com.bo/anteriores/20040921/santacruz_8.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-04-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110208004629/http://www.eldeber.com.bo/anteriores/20040921/santacruz_8.html |archivedate=2011-02-08 |df= }}</ref>
==Bibliography== Mayser is the author of ''Alto Paragua: Verdaderas Guerrillas Bolivianas'', an account of the struggle of the FSB against the [[Revolutionary Nationalist Movement]] government.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eldiario.net/noticias/2009/2009_02/nt090218/1_01opn.php|title=Noticias EL DIARIO - Primera página|work=eldiario.net}}</ref> He has also authored ''Santa Cruz y sus provincias''.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eldeber.com.bo/anteriores/20050408/santacruz_4.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-04-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081014174506/http://www.eldeber.com.bo/anteriores/20050408/santacruz_4.html |archivedate=2008-10-14 |df= }}</ref>
